srcLoc: *mtmInterplantData.csv: Defines source and destination locations between which mtm's  *can be moved
destLoc: along with the time and cost of the move.

srcLoc: *srcLoc: string. Source Location. Name of location mtm will be moved from.
*destLoc: string. Destination Location. Name of location where mtm can be moved to.*defaultMoveCost: float >=0. cost to move mtm from srcLoc to .
*defaultMoveTime: float >=0. time in periods that it takes to move mtm from srcLoc to *destLoc.
*An interplant mtm move operation will be defined for any mtm defined in mtmData that *has its plantLoc equal to a srcLoc in this file.
